      "text": "🤷Just because PowerShell works on Linux does not mean that all PowerShell commands work on Linux.\n\nServices aren't technically a thing on Linux (they're Daemons)\n\nGet-LocalUser and Get-LocalGroup are also Windows-specific commands.\n\nIf you actually want linux alternatives, just ask."
